<html>

<head>

  <title>Patty Alert</title>

  <link href="css/grid.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
  <link href="css/main.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />

  <script data-main="scripts/main" src="scripts/vendor/require.js"></script>

</head>

<body>

  <div class="status sighting"
    data-0="opacity:1;"
    data-200="opacity:0;">
    <h1>EAT ALL THE CHICKEN PATTIES</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="main"
    data-0="margin-top: 17em;"
    data-200="margin-top: 0em;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header row">
        <div class="col-12 header">
          <div class="hero <%= @level %>">
            <h1>Patty Alert Level: <span class="level"><%= @level %></span></h1>
            <p>Wecome to the Marist College Chicken Patty Alert System (CPAS).</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="signup" class="col-8">
          <img class="loader" src="img/loader.gif" />
        </div>

        <div class="col-4">
          <h2>But seriously...</h2>
          <p>What's the deal here?</p>
          <p>Look we love Chicken Patties... they're like the bee's knees. Unfortunately unless you go to the cafeteria every day, it's hard to catch Chicken Patty day.</p>
          <p>We monitor the cafeteria website and sightings in the wild to keep you informed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer row">
        <p class="col-12">brought to you by colby, dan & justin</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<!-- templates -->
<%= erb(:signup, :layout => false) %>
<%= erb(:confirm, :layout => false) %>

</body>

</html>